   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00007"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00008"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Vladimir:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00009"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00010"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00011"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Whare are all these corpses from?
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00012"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00013"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Estragon:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00014"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00015"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00016"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>These skeletons.
      </text>
     </text-unit>
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00017"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00018"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>. . .
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00019"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00020"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Vladimir:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00021"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00022"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00023"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>A charnel-house! A charnel-house!(Waiting for Godot, 41)
      </text>
     </text-unit>
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00024"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00025"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>[ Estragon has exited offstage to right and left and come ‘‘panting’’ back and fallen into Vladimir’s arms.
       <Em xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
          id="ID.00026"
         >
        <?MarkedContent page="1" ?> —Ed.
       </Em>
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?> ]
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00027"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00028"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Estragon:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00029"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00030"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00031"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>I’m in hell!
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00032"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00033"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Vladimir:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00034"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00035"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00036"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Where were you?
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00037"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00038"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Estragon:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00039"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00040"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00041"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>They’re coming there too!
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
   <LI xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
      id="ID.00042"
     >
    <Lbl xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00043"
      >
     <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>Vladimir:
    </Lbl>
    <LBody xmlns="http://iso.org/pdf2/ssn"
       id="ID.00044"
      >
     <text-unit xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
        id="ID.00045"
        rolemaps-to="Part"
       >
      <text xmlns="https://www.latex-project.org/ns/dflt"
         id="ID.00046"
         xmlns:Layout="http://iso.org/pdf/ssn/Layout"
         Layout:TextAlign="Justify"
         rolemaps-to="P"
        >
       <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>We’re surrounded! [Estragon makes a rush towards back.] Imbe­cile! There’s no way out there. [He takes Estragon by the arms and drags him towards front. Gesture towards front.] There! Not a soul in sight! Off you go! Quick! [He pushes Estragon towards auditorium. Estragon recoils in horror.] You won’t? [He contemplates auditorium.] Well I can under­stand that. Wait till I see. [He reflects.] Your only hope left is to disappear. (47)
      </text>
     </text-unit>
    </LBody>
   </LI>
  </list>
 </text-unit>
</Document>
